        [
          "You have built a good life for yourself in LA. You have a small amount of influence in the media locally. Build it up to both protect yourself and gain respect."
        ],
        [
          "Your sire has become a liability to your new life and you know it. He's powerful enough you can't directly challenge him, but as he has others who hunt you, you can have people who hunt him. Use your influence to find someone willing to do it for you."
